outside his office.

1445
01:07:24,687 --> 01:07:28,054
I think she was arrested
for stalking him or something.

1446
01:07:33,062 --> 01:07:34,529
<i>Do you still love him?</i>

1447
01:07:34,630 --> 01:07:36,291
I'll die loving him.

1448
01:07:36,399 --> 01:07:38,594
I never got married
because of him.

1449
01:07:50,913 --> 01:07:54,246
I'm the incurable romantic,
you know?

1450
01:07:54,350 --> 01:07:57,183
The idea of marrying somebody
that I didn't love

1451
01:07:57,286 --> 01:07:59,516
and having to sleep with him
and have his kids

1452
01:07:59,622 --> 01:08:04,116
and live a humdrum, blasé life
with half a love...

1453
01:08:04,227 --> 01:08:08,061
I would rather have
a short few weeks

1454
01:08:08,164 --> 01:08:13,602
with someone who was
the star in the crown

1455
01:08:13,703 --> 01:08:17,662
than to spend my life
with someone and be miserable.

1456
01:08:17,774 --> 01:08:20,265
Love is not a changing thing.

1457
01:08:20,376 --> 01:08:23,243
It doesn't... it's a steadfast
and eternal thing.

1458
01:08:23,346 --> 01:08:24,836
It's like an eternal flame.

1459
01:08:24,947 --> 01:08:28,144
It doesn't just stop because
of circumstances or situations.

1460
01:08:28,251 --> 01:08:29,650
It goes on, even past death.

1461
01:08:29,752 --> 01:08:32,585
It's a very bleak future
you paint for yourself.

1462
01:08:32,688 --> 01:08:33,780
What is gonna happen to you?

1463
01:08:33,890 --> 01:08:36,222
Well, first of all,
I want to write my book

1464
01:08:36,325 --> 01:08:38,816
and make sure
that the truth comes out,

1465
01:08:38,928 --> 01:08:41,123
because, regardless
of what you've heard,

1466
01:08:41,230 --> 01:08:44,131
I haven't sold my life story
to anyone, to any newspapers.

1467
01:08:44,233 --> 01:08:46,895
<i>The only newspaper I have talked
to has been the Express,</i>

1468
01:08:47,003 --> 01:08:49,198
who did the article about
my adventures in America,

1469
01:08:49,305 --> 01:08:50,363
and that's it.

1470
01:08:50,473 --> 01:08:51,940
And I want my story to be told.

1471
01:08:52,041 --> 01:08:53,872
Are you really prepared
to condemn yourself,

1472
01:08:53,976 --> 01:08:57,673
'cause that's what it is,
to a very solitary life?

1473
01:08:57,780 --> 01:08:59,042
Yes.

